# Winston Log Files Directory

This directory contains application log files generated by Winston logger.

## Log Files

- `application-YYYY-MM-DD.log` - All application logs (info, warn, error)
- `error-YYYY-MM-DD.log` - Error logs only
- `exceptions-YYYY-MM-DD.log` - Uncaught exception logs
- `rejections-YYYY-MM-DD.log` - Unhandled promise rejection logs

## Retention Policy

- Application logs: 14 days
- Error logs: 30 days
- Exceptions: 30 days
- Rejections: 30 days

## Auto-Rotation

- Max file size: 20MB
- Rotation: Daily
- Compression: Enabled (gzip)

## Git

Log files are excluded from version control (.gitignore).
This directory structure is preserved with .gitkeep.
